Behold a delightful pixel art spectacle—the HackDavis stage aglow! Shimmering gold "HD 25" balloons float above, each pixel gleaming like precious nuggets. A rustic wooden podium, like a hero’s stand, radiates warmth, topped with the daintiest pixel-posies in pastel hues, a garden in miniature.

Behind, a vibrant digital screen buzzes, its greenish-blue pixels pulsing with the energy of the countdown. Blue and yellow ribbons dance across the scene, adding playful vibes, while the black stage drape grounds the scene in mystery.

Below, the HackDavis banner is a pixel dream, overflowing with smiling bunnies, fluffy clouds, and lush green pixels, all for "social good." The American flag waves in the background, a pixelated symbol of freedom, and the "NORTHEAST" clock ticks on, reminding us of time's precious passage in this world of code and creation. The scene bursts with joyous pixels, inviting everyone to dive into a world of tech and dreams.
